metadata.name: ET #1
metadata.description:
Memento Mori. Time is the great equalizer - the skull representing the elimination of differences between people.
Within the symbol of the skull in Shakespeare's Hamlet we remember the inevitability of life's conclusion... so we choose to make the very most of what we have now.
Our collection offers a 555-piece set of original creations, ultra unique digital collectibles housed on the Ethereum blockchain.
A range of art which draws inspiration from the many facets of life's wonders. Each limited item strives for design excellence, this collection of one of a kind skullish items is made for those who move boldly through life..
..always remembering that time is of the highest essence.
100% of taxes from this collection go to support the Skull Finance token through strategic buyback and burns - transitioning ultimately to become a fund which drives the Skull Finance ecosystem.
Become a Scullionare - step into the dynamic world of the Skull community.
